(221, 'ÅAlexandreuvß', 'from (the city so called)', 'Alexandreus', 'None', 'al-ex-and-reuce\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'from Alexandreia (the city so called); an Alexandreian or inhabitant of Alexandria:--of Alexandria, Alexandrian.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a native or resident of Alexandria in Egypt</OL>'),
