(503, 'ajntofqalmevw', 'from a compound of (473) and (3788)', 'antophthalmeo', 'None', 'ant-of-thal-meh\'-o', 'Verb', 'from a compound of «473» and «3788»; to face:--bear up into.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to look against or straight at<LI>metaph. to bear up against, withstand</OL>'),
