(514, 'a[xioß', 'probably from (71)', 'axios', '1:379,63', 'ax\'-ee-os', 'Adjective', 'probably from «71»; deserving, comparable or suitable (as if drawing praise):--due reward, meet, (un-)worthy.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>weighing, having weight, having the weight of another thing of like value, worth as much<LI>befitting, congruous, corresponding to a thing<LI>of one who has merited anything worthy<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>both in a good and a bad sense</OL></OL>'),
