(516, 'ajxivwß', 'from (514)', 'axios', 'None', 'ax-ee\'-oce', 'Adverb', 'adverb from «514»; appropriately:--as becometh, after a godly sort, worthily(-thy).', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>suitably, worthily, in a manner worthy of</OL>'),
