(526, 'ajpallotriovw', 'from (575) and a derivative of (245)', 'apallotrioo', '1:265,43', 'ap-al-lot-ree-o\'-o', 'Verb', 'from «575» and a derivative of «245»; to estrange away, i.e. (passively and figuratively) to be non-participant:-- alienate, be alien.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to alienate, estrange<LI>to be shut out from one\'s fellowship and intimacy</OL>'),
(527, 'aJpalovß', 'of uncertain derivation', 'apalos', 'None', 'ap-al-os\'', 'Adjective', 'of uncertain derivation; soft:--tender.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>tender<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>of a branch of a tree that is full of sap</OL></OL>'),
(528, 'ajpantavw', 'from (575) and a derivative of (473)', 'apantao', 'None', 'ap-an-tah\'-o', 'Verb', 'from «575» and a derivative of «473»; to meet away, i.e. encounter:--meet.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to go to meet, to meet<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>in a military sense: a hostile meeting</OL></OL>'),
