(533, 'ajparnevomai', 'from (575) and (720)', 'aparneomai', '1:471,*', 'ap-ar-neh\'-om-ahee', 'Verb', 'from «575» and «720»; to deny utterly, i.e. disown, abstain:--deny.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to deny<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>to affirm that one has no acquaintance or connection with someone<LI>to forget one\'s self, lose sight of one\'s self and one\'s own interests</OL></OL>'),
