(572, 'aJplovthß', 'from (573)', 'haplotes', '1:386,65', 'hap-lot\'-ace', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «573»; singleness, i.e. (subjectively) sincerity (without dissimulation or self-seeking), or (objectively) generosity (copious bestowal):--bountifulness, liberal(-ity), simplicity, singleness.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>singleness, simplicity, sincerity, mental honesty<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>the virtue of one who is free from pretence and hypocrisy</OL><LI>not self seeking, openness of heart manifesting itself by generousity</OL>'),
