(595, 'ajpovqesiß', 'from (659)', 'apothesis', 'None', 'ap-oth\'-es-is', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «659»; a laying aside (literally or figuratively):--putting away (off).', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a putting off or away</OL>'),
