(1102, 'gnafeuvß', 'by variation for a derivative from knapto (to tease cloth)', 'gnapheus', 'None', 'gnaf-yuce\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'by variation for a derivative from knapto (to tease cloth); a cloth-dresser:--fuller.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a fuller</OL>'),
