(1301, 'diathrevw', 'from (1223) and (5083)', 'diatereo', '8:151,1174', 'dee-at-ay-reh\'-o', 'Verb', 'from «1223» and «5083»; to watch thoroughly, i.e. (positively and transitively) to observe strictly, or (negatively and reflexively) to avoid wholly:--keep.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to keep continually or carefully</OL>'),
