(4406, 'prwvi>moß', 'from (4404)', 'proimos', 'None', 'pro\'-ee-mos', 'Adjective', 'from «4404»; dawning, i.e. (by analogy) autumnal (showering, the first of the rainy season):--early.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>early<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>of the early rain which fell from October on</OL></OL>'),
