(4417, 'ptaivw', 'a form of (4098)', 'ptaio', '6:883,968', 'ptah\'-yo', 'Verb', 'a form of «4098»; to trip, i.e. (figuratively) to err, sin, fail (of salvation):--fall, offend, stumble.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to cause one to stumble or fall<LI>to stumble<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>to err, make a mistake, to sin<LI>to fall into misery, become wretched</OL></OL>'),
