(4424, 'Ptolemai?ß', 'from Ptolemaios (Ptolemy, after whom it was named)', 'Ptolemais', 'None', 'ptol-em-ah-is\'', 'Noun Location', 'from Ptolemaios (Ptolemy, after whom it was named); Ptolemais, a place in Palestine:--Ptolemais.', 'Ptolemais or Accho = \"warlike\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a maritime city of Phoenicia, which got its name, apparently, from Ptolemy Lathyrus, who captured it 103 BC, and rebuilt it more beautifully</OL>'),
