(4451, 'puvrwsiß', 'from (4448)', 'purosis', '6:950,975', 'poo\'-ro-sis', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «4448»; ignition, i.e. (specially), smelting (figuratively, conflagration, calamity as a test):--burning, trial.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a burning<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>the burning by which metals are roasted and reduced<LI>by a figure drawn from a refiners fire<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>calamities or trials that test the character</OL></OL></OL>'),
(4452, '-pw', 'another form of the base of (4458)', 'po', 'None', 'po', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>yet, even<LI>used only in compound with words 3369, 3380, 3764, 3768, 4455</OL>', 'another form of the base of «4458»; an enclitic particle of indefiniteness; yet, even; used only in the comparative. See «3369», «3380», «3764», «3768», «4455».', ''),
(4453, 'pwlevw', 'probably ultimately from pelomai (to be busy, to trade)', 'poleo', 'None', 'po-leh\'-o', 'Verb', 'probably ultimately from pelomai (to be busy, to trade); to barter (as a pedlar), i.e. to sell:--sell, whatever is sold.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to barter, to sell<LI>sellers</OL>'),
(4454, 'pw\'loß', 'apparently a primary word', 'polos', '6:959,981', 'po\'-los', 'Noun Masculine', 'apparently a primary word; a \"foal\" or \"filly\", i.e. (specially), a young ass:--colt.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a colt, the young of a horse<LI>a young creature<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>of a young ass<LI>an ass\'s colt</OL></OL>'),
