(5316, 'faivnw', 'prolongation for the base of (5457)', 'phaino', '9:1,1244', 'fah\'-ee-no', 'Verb', 'prolongation for the base of «5457»; to lighten (shine), i.e. show (transitive or intransitive, literal or figurative):-- appear, seem, be seen, shine, × think.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to bring forth into the light, cause to shine, shed light<LI>shine<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>to shine, be bright or resplendent<LI>to become evident, to be brought forth into the light, come to view, appear<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>of growing vegetation, to come to light<LI>to appear, be seen<LI>exposed to view</OL><LI>to meet the eyes, strike the sight, become clear or manifest<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be seen, appear</OL><LI>to appear to the mind, seem to one\'s judgment or opinion</OL></OL>'),
