(5323, 'Fanouhvl', 'of Hebrew origin (06439)', 'Phanouel', 'None', 'fan-oo-ale\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'of Hebrew origin («06439»); Phanuel (i.e. Penuel), an Israelite:--Phanuel.', 'Phanuel = \"the face of God\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>the father of Anna, the prophetess of the tribe of Asher</OL>'),
