(5578, 'yeudoprofhvthß', 'from (5571) and (4396)', 'pseudoprophetes', '6:781,952', 'psyoo-dop-rof-ay\'-tace', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «5571» and «4396»; a spurious prophet, i.e. pretended foreteller or religious impostor:--false prophet.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>one who, acting the part of a divinely inspired prophet, utters falsehoods under the name of divine prophecies<LI>a false prophet</OL>'),
