(5598, 'W', 'a primitive word', 'omega', '1:1,*', 'o\'-meg-ah', 'Noun', 'the last letter of the Greek alphabet, i.e. (figuratively) the finality:--Omega.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>the last letter in the Greek alphabet<LI>the last</OL>'),
