(5600, 'w\\', 'the subjunctive of (1510)', 'o', 'None', 'o,', 'Verb', 'the subjunctive of «1510»; (may, might, can, could, would, should, must, etc.; also with «1487» and its comparative, as well as with other particles) be:--+ appear, are, (may, might,  should) be, × have, is, + pass the flower of her age, should stand, were.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>be, may be, etc.</OL>'),
